=Episode 15=

12
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:19,420
(Follow your heart.
Don't limit yourself.)

13
00:02:28,410 --> 00:02:29,270
Perfect.

14
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:32,990
Cen Jin.

15
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,930
Once this ad goes live,

16
00:02:37,230 --> 00:02:38,450
