79
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:07,950
(begins with you writing it yourself.)

80
00:05:08,930 --> 00:05:09,800
(Write boldly.)

81
00:05:09,888 --> 00:05:11,270
(I'll always be rooting for you.)

82
